---
title: Honey & Lemon Glazed Chicken with Spinach & Leek Colcannon
description: We’ve updated the classic Irish side dish of colcannon by adding leek and spinach to the mashed potatoes for a comforting yet unique take on your meal. With a sweet and zesty glazed chicken plus feta-topped beans, this meal is the tastiest way to get your greens!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c19e65ac445fa2da56f6cd2-0aaacf96.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/honey-lemon-glazed-chicken-5c19e65ac445fa2da56f6cd2-04ed3f9d.pdf
cuisine: Modern
